data.description: This light-filled home boasts a great layout, tons of curb appeal and a detached garage with new workshop addition. With a little over 2000 sq ft, this property offers a spacious living room and dining room with vaulted ceiling leading to a private back deck overlooking the woods. The kitchen features new appliances, ample cabinet space, custom shelving and room for a breakfast table. The first floor also includes an owner’s suite with walk-in closet and bath with double vanities and two additional bedrooms served by a hall bath. The second floor loft with half bath makes a great office, game room or additional sleep space. The detached garage has been recently improved with additional workshop space, a mini-split hvac, new dry wall and floor drain. This property is in the Mallard Bay community which offers amenities to include a waterfront pool, private dock with boat slips, boat ramp, tennis courts and dog park. This home is served by Breezeline internet.
